Package com.poesys.db.dao.query

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    IKeyListQuerySql<T extends IDbDto>
    An interface that defines the set of operations required by an IQueryListWithKeyList object to build and parameterize a SQL SELECT statement for a set of data transfer objects (DTOs) specified by a list of key values associated with the SQL statement through an IN clause.
    IKeyQuerySql<T extends IDbDto>
    An interface that defines the set of operations required by an IQueryByKey object to build and parameterize a SQL SELECT statement for an IDto.
    IParameterizedCountSql<P extends IDbDto>
    An interface that defines the set of operations required by an IQueryCount object to build and parameterize a SQL SELECT statement that returns an integer count of a set of objects specified by a set of parameters defined in an IDto of type P
    IParameterizedQuerySql<T extends IDbDto,P extends IDbDto>
    An interface that defines the set of operations required by an IQueryListWithParameters object to build and parameterize a SQL SELECT statement for a set of data transfer objects (DTOs) specified by a set of parameters defined in a second DTO
    IQueryByKey<T extends IDbDto>
    An interface for Command-pattern data access objects (DAOs) that query by a key within a data transfer object (DTO)
    IQueryCount<P extends IDbDto>
    An interface for Command data access objects (DAOs) that query a count of some kind based on a set of parameters contained in an IDto of type P
    IQueryList<T extends IDbDto>
    An interface for a Command class that queries a list of data transfer objects (DTOs)
    IQueryListWithParameters<T extends IDbDto,S extends IDbDto,C extends java.util.Collection<T>>
    An interface for a Command class that queries a list of data transfer objects (DTOs).
    IQuerySql<T extends IDbDto>
    An interface that defines the set of operations required by an IQueryList object to build a SQL SELECT statement for a set of data transfer objects (DTOs)
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    QueryByKey<T extends IDbDto>
    An implementation of the IQueryByKey interface that implements the basic elements of a query by primary key.
    QueryCacheByKey<T extends IDbDto>
    An implementation of the IQueryByKey interface that implements the basic elements of a query by primary key including caching.
    QueryCacheList<T extends IDbDto>
    An implementation of the IQueryList interface that implements the basic elements of a query of multiple objects including caching.
    QueryCacheListWithKeyList<T extends IDbDto>
    An implementation of the IQueryList interface that implements the basic elements of a query of multiple objects including caching using a list of primary keys in an IN clause.
    QueryCacheListWithParameters<T extends IDbDto,S extends IDbDto,C extends java.util.Collection<T>>
    An implementation of the IQueryListWithParameters interface that implements the basic elements of a query of multiple objects including caching.
    QueryCount<P extends IDbDto>
    An implementation of the IQueryCount interface that performs the basic count query given a parameter data transfer object (DTO) of type P
    QueryDatabaseCacheByKey<T extends IDbDto>
    An implementation of the IQueryByKey interface that implements the basic elements of a query by primary key including caching, but with direct query of the database instead of checking the cache first, thus refreshing the cache.
    QueryDatabaseMemcachedByKey<T extends IDbDto>
    An implementation of the IQueryByKey interface that implements the basic elements of a query by primary key including caching in the distributed memcached server.
    QueryList<T extends IDbDto>
    An implementation of the IQueryList interface that queries a list of data transfer objects (DTOs) based on a SQL statement with no parameters.
    QueryListWithKeyList<T extends IDbDto>
    An implementation of the IQueryList interface that queries a list of data transfer objects (DTOs) based on a parameterized SQL statement and a list of keys.
    QueryListWithParameters<T extends IDbDto,S extends IDbDto,C extends java.util.Collection<T>>
    An implementation of the IQueryListWithParameters interface that queries a list of data transfer objects (DTOs) based on a parameterized SQL statement.
    QueryMemcachedByKey<T extends IDbDto>
    An implementation of the IQueryByKey interface that implements the basic elements of a query by primary key including caching in the distributed memcached server.
    QueryMemcachedList<T extends IDbDto>
    An implementation of the IQueryList interface that implements the basic elements of a query of multiple objects including caching using the distributing caching system memcached.
    QueryMemcachedListWithKeyList<T extends IDbDto>
    An implementation of the IQueryList interface that implements the basic elements of a query of multiple objects including caching using the distributing caching system memcached.
    QueryMemcachedListWithParameters<T extends IDbDto,S extends IDbDto,C extends java.util.Collection<T>>
    An implementation of the IQueryListWithParameters interface that implements the basic elements of a query of multiple objects including caching.
